hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections

Class LinkedListIndexedCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections.Collection
      • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections.LinkedListIndexedCollection

  • public class LinkedListIndexedCollection
extends Collection
    Collection that stores it's elements into a linked list. Provides all services collections offer. Can contain multiples of an element. Does not contain null elements.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Juraj Pejnovic
